
### Define DDMC-specific variables
#
### Define preprocessor parameter
PPDEFINE FLASH_GREY_DDMC

### Grid variable to contain DDMC flag
VARIABLE TRAP TYPE: PER_VOLUME

### Face variable for momentum deposition
FACEVAR DDFX
FACEVAR DDFY
FACEVAR DDFZ

### Cell-centered variables for storing average depo
VARIABLE DDMX TYPE: PER_MASS
VARIABLE DDMY TYPE: PER_MASS
VARIABLE DDMZ TYPE: PER_MASS

### Leakage opacities for grey DDMC
SCRATCHVAR KLEX
SCRATCHVAR KLEY
SCRATCHVAR KLEZ
#SCRATCHFACEXVAR KLEX
#SCRATCHFACEYVAR KLEY
#SCRATCHFACEZVAR KLEZ
